<section class="pitaco-participar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="participar-card">
      <h2 class="title">COMO PARTICIPAR?</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p class="description">
        Combinamos todos os nossos encontros por meio da <strong
          >comunidade no WhatsApp</strong
        >. Para participar, basta entrar lá e acompanhar as informações
        compartilhadas no grupo.
      </p>
      <p class="description">
        É nesse espaço que organizamos metas, horários e detalhes dos encontros,
        facilitando a comunicação e garantindo que todas as pessoas interessadas
        possam se manter informadas e participar das atividades.
      </p>

      <div class="action-wrapper">
        <a
          href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/E7Ip1usVgay3cxtX2UZ7rt"
          class="btn-pitaco"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="whatsapp-icon"
            ><path
              d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Entrar na Comunidade
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pitaco-participar {
    padding: 100px 2rem 140px 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      var(--bg-page-light, #f5f5f5) 0%,
      #e8eaf6 100%
    );
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .participar-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(40, 58, 134, 0.15);
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid rgba(40, 58, 134, 0.08);
    padding: 4rem 5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .participar-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #283a86, #7adb53, #283a86);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: gradientPanLine 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    color: #283a86;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #283a86, #7adb53, #283a86);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: gradientPanLine 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @keyframes gradientPanLine {
    0% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .description strong {
    color: #283a86;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .action-wrapper {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .btn-pitaco {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background-color: #7adb53;
    color: #0c1430;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(122, 219, 83, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
  }

  .btn-pitaco:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(122, 219, 83, 0.5);
    background-color: #8bed65;
  }

  /* --- RESPONSIVIDADE MOBILE --- */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .participar-card {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
